 premiere on May 8, 2020.<ref name=\"SeriesPremiereDate\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/hulu-premiere-dates-the-great-ramy-solar-opposites-1202833786/|title=Hulu Sets Premiere Dates For 'The Great', 'Ramy' And 'Solar Opposites' \u2013 TCA|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|date=January 17, 2020|accessdate=January 17, 2020}}</ref>\n\n===Casting===\nAlongside the series order announcement, it was confirmed that [[Justin Roiland]], [[Sean Giambrone]], and [[Mary Mack (comedian)|Mary Mack]] would voice the lead characters in the series.<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\"/><ref name=\"SeriesOrder2\"/><ref name=\"SeriesOrder3\"/>\n\n===Marketing===\nThe first teaser for the series was released on March 25, 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Solar Opposites - Teaser (Official) \u2022 A Hulu Original |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tLjo8IQLa9o |website=www.youtube.com |publisher=YouTube |accessdate=25 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb title|8910922}}\n\n{{Hulu}}\n\n[[Category:American animated sitcoms]]\n[[Category:American adult animated comic science fiction television series]]\n[[Category:Animated television series about extraterrestrial life]]\n[[Category:Animated television series about families]]\n[[Category:Hulu original programming]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Television series by Fox Television Animation]]\n[[Category:Television series created by Justin Roiland]]\n[[Category:Television series by Justin Roiland's Solo Vanity Card Productions!]]\n[[Category:Television series by 20th Century Fox Television]]\n[[Category:Upcoming animated television series]]\n[[Category:Upcoming comedy television series]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American sitcom}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Solar Opposites\n| image              = \n| caption            = \n| genre              = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Adult animation]]\n* [[Television comedy|Comedy]]\n* [[Anim