ons]]\n[[Category:Horned deities]]\n[[Category:Assyrian art and architecture]]\n", "name_user": "Oshanna11", "label": "safe", "comment": "Minor grammar issue", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lamassu"}
